However, MK went out and thoroughly searched the white house, to no avail. MK hoped that Buttons' fear would eventually be overcome by hunger, so she alerted her neighbors to be on the lookout for Buttons or any sound he might make.<\/hatul><hatul>Several days later, her neighbors in the white house heard a sound coming up from underneath them and alerted MK.
